com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Interface ClassDataForClassificationService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultClassDataForClassificationService

    public interface ClassDataForClassificationService

    This service enables you to create, read, update and delete class data, that is valid on a given date.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_CLFN_CLASS_SRV
    API Version:1
    Communication Scenario:Classification Systems OData Integration (SAP_COM_0163)
